{"word":"αἴτιος","slug":"αἴτιος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>αἴτιος, α, ον</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:αἰτία\">αἰτία</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pert. to\">pert. to</a> being causative (of/for)’, <b><i>reason</i></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ nt.\">nt.</a> noun <b><a href='B:510 19:40'>Ac 19:40</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ sim.\">sim.</a> <el>αἰ. ϑανάτου</el> <i>reason for imposing the death penalty</i> <b><a href='B:490 23:22'>Lk 23:22</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ masc.\">masc.</a> noun in sense of <i>one responsible (for)</i> <b><a href='B:650 5:9'>Hb 5:9</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ nt.\">nt.</a> noun also in the sense <b><i>something chargeable, crime</i> <a href='B:490 23:4'>Lk 23:4</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:αἰτιάομαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:αἰτίωμα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}